{"tid":1052732,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人睇過Myself Yourself呢套舊番? 都幾出色","createTime":"2019-03-08T13:34:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-11T14:27:26.000Z","uid":75100,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"78dcaebb4ea723e7c0e66a1718b8ca7c4e3f9694","tid":1052732,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:34:06.000Z","msg":"都係男主角細個離開左故鄉，然後大左返去，再遇返各位舊友人既老套背景，呢套野2007年的，但我都完全接受到佢既畫風<br />\n<br />\n開頭以為係d後宮番，d女圍住相認，見到男主角就臉紅心跳加快想表白<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />本身諗住無腦睇，點知同我想像中都幾唔同........<br />\n<br />\n中間開始，每集都會有轉折點同爆點，會令你期待下集係點，同埋唔會話有特別悶既集數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n劇情走向，都有包含d好多人都鐘意既「黑化」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同埋唔會話有d角色路人化，大部份角色都描繪得好生動，都有屬於佢地既戲份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n整體都幾好睇，但13集真係有d少，我覺得埋尾可以再講多d男主角同菜菜香既故事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iVX1s6W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiVX1s6W.png&h=6fe2e131&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"254f680e041a3519ac8dfb21395732593d2c3aa0","tid":1052732,"uid":146340,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T13:42:55.000Z","msg":"55"},{"pid":"8c202c96e1f1a7718277a98fbe60637794c55ae1","tid":1052732,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"無人睇過? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a857b2c0e96e5d8494d2e6d339ff136099cd51fb","tid":1052732,"uid":34293,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8c202c96e1f1a7718277a98fbe60637794c55ae1","tid":1052732,"uid":75100,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-03-08T15:06:13.000Z","msg":"無人睇過? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=